title: Its Not What You Think, Immigration and the U.S.; The Warren Markowitz Show, Politically Incorrect, 10/24/2017
description: The Warren Markowitz Show, It's My World You Just Live In It. A soap box for Independent Ideas, current events and politics of the day. America, is rapidly following the paths of many failed empires, and not for the reasons you might think. Join me and lets take a look at the impact that outside influence has on the U.S. and its future.
